1. generate high entropy password with gpg
gpg --gen-random --armor 2 64 > vc_pass.txt

2. encrypt the password with gpg
gpg --encrypt --recipient YOURKEYID vc_pass.txt

3. move vc_pass to usb
move vc_pass.txt.gpg X:\vc_pass.txt.gpg

4. shred plain text password in windows:
in powershell:
# Overwrite with random bytes
$bytes = new-object byte[] 2048
(new-object Random).NextBytes($bytes)
[IO.File]::WriteAllBytes("vc_pass.txt", $bytes)

# Delete the file
Remove-Item "vc_pass.txt" -Force
